title: No option to purchase transfer server
body: I moved from aussie to NA and there is no option to purchase account transfer and I'm stuck playing in high ping.  I know you click account and there should be options as I do see them in North America server, but not Oceania.  I only see "Summoner name change" purchase, nothing else.  Anyone else have the same issue?

replies.body: did you guys found any solution to this? stuck with the same problem
i have the same problem too .i wanna transfer my account from EUW to EUNE i can't find the option there is only summoner's name change
Yeah i have the same problem. I transferred my account to EU-W, but i want to transfer to another server but there is no option at all

There were a few issues preventing players from getting their accounts transferred out of OCE, but we should be able to make that happen in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) if you still haven't been able to get your account moved over.
